    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning! Honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it; it's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. It drives like a dream and looks flawless inside and out. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new without the crazy dealership prices, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you'll fall in love!",
