    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection, and the variable M differential lock provides exceptional exit traction. No modifications, no deferred maintenance, and a completely clean underside. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Professional inspection welcome.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
