    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with original factory paint that has been meticulously protected with a ceramic coating; you will not find a single stone chip, door ding, or swirl mark. The alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash, and wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather upholstery is supple, free of any bolster wear or creases, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface operates with factory-spec precision, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive service history included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
