      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains entirely unblemished. This is a definitive example of the model, offering an unparalleled driving experience for those who demand nothing short of perfection. Inspection confirms it is in pristine, investment-grade state.",
