    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition! I have babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s basically flawless inside and out. It drives like it just rolled off the lot, and I\u2019ve kept up with every single service. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! I'm so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. Let's get you a test drive!",
      "price": 44500.0,
