    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exceptional power-to-weight ratio. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells, and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry is factory-spec with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in the chassis is known for. With zero oxidation and a pristine interior, this is a mechanically flawless example of a modern classic.",
